        'description': 'üåµSaguaro National Park\nWe just love cacti! Heck, we even have a small one that travels around with us in our RV. His name is Sir Richard Johnson III and let\'s just say he\'s a bit smaller and lacks the appendages that this big guy has.\n\nIt was another beautiful sunset here in Arizona and we\'re looking to head a bit further West in the next few days. Looking towards Yuma/Mittry Lake area so if you\'re in the area or heading that way, please let us know if you want to meet up.\n\n#tinywheelhouse #cactus #saguaro #nationalparks #saguaronationalpark #nps #visitarizona #ditchingsuburbia #fulltimers #fulltimerv #gorving #sunset #rvlife #nomadlife #nomad #rvlifestyle #rvliving #rvliving #nomadliving #wildwildwest #western #west #nationalparkgeek'
