          'description': 'üî•üí¶ Hot Springs\nMy ladies loved the rooftop hot springs at the Charles Motel in Truth or Consequences, NM. I have to say that Molly in particular loved it but we think she is part dolphin or sea monkey or something. The Charles is the most economical place to soak and was kind enough to not charge for Molly, which most places would. They also take credit cards... which most places in T or C don\'t. I have to be honest, I can\'t wait for cash only businesses to just go away... 2.75% is a reasonable cost of doing business and if you your business can\'t survive with that cost then it probably isn\'t a good business model to begin with. End Rant.\n\n<span class="hashtags">#visitnewmexico #nm #torc #truthorconsequences #hotsprings #jacuzzi #toddler #toddlerlife #swimming #family #gorving #ditchingsuburbia #fulltimers #fulltimefamily #fulltimefamilies</span>'
