          'description': 'New Mexican Apple Pie a la Mode\nI\'m not one to take photos of food but this is probably the most unique and delicious pie I\'ve ever had. This is not just your standard apple... At the Pie Town Cafe, in addition to apples they have roasted green chiles and pi√±ons. It\'s the perfect mix of sweet and spicy especially served with ice cream. If you\'re ever in the area of Pie Town, New Mexico, you should absolutely drop in for a slice or heck grab a whole pie!\n\n#pie #pietown #applepie #red #newMexico #alamode #fulltimers #gorving #travelNM #greenchile #pi√±on #fulltimefamily #food #foodporn #dessert #dessertporn'
