          'description': '$30/night\nNot a bad price for front row action first thing this morning! Though Molly is a little more interested in watching Tayo on her iPad. \n#gorving #fulltimers #fulltimefamily #xscapers #escapees #abq #abqballoonfiesta #balloons #balloonfiesta #rvlife #rvliving #rvlifestyle #toddlerlife'
