          'description': 'That\'s One Angry Bird‚Ñ¢\nReally glad we decided to watch from the RV this morning because this guy came down right by us! It was rather event-filled with numerous balloons landing and actually launching right near us since many RVs have left or moved closer to the fiesta. \n#abq #abqballoonfiesta #albuquerque #balloonfiesta #balloons #angrybirds #hotairballoons #gorving #fulltimefamily #fulltimers #xscapers #escapees'
