          'description': 'üá∫üá∏ Team America üá∫üá∏\nThey say these colors don\'t run but apparently they do... They run on propane! \n#america #usa #starsandstripes #bluesky #abq #abqballoonfiesta #balloons #hotairballoons #gorving #nomads #fulltimers #fulltimefamily #xscapers #escapees #ditchingsuburbia #balloonfiesta #freedom'
