          'description': 'The force is strong with this balloon\nOk, so I\'m kind of a Star Wars geek and this balloon makes my inner 5 year old want to run around in a brown towel and make lightsaber noises while wielding a foam pool noodle. \n#starwars #yoda #abq #albuquerque #abqballoonfiesta #theforce #theforceisstrongwiththisone #nomads #gorving #fulltimers #ditchingsuburbia #rvlife #rvliving #fulltimefamily #balloon #hotairballoon'
