          'description': 'Splish splash Molly was takin\' a salt bath\nOk so Molly *LOVED* the salt flats. She went a splishin\' and a splashin\' all over the place. It was almost hard to keep up! She learned the hard way about salt water in the eyes but she just kept trucking. She also figured out that the water tasted awful but continued to try to drink it. All in all this has to be one of the best places we\'ve camped thus far in the RV. \n#bonnevillesaltflats #toddler #toddlerlife #rvlife #fulltimers #fulltimefamilies #nomads #toddlerfun #swimming #splash #utah #bonneville #ditchingsuburbia #gorving #saltflats'
