          'description': 'Bonneville Salt Flats\nThe last time Anne and I were out here we took our Honda Fit out several miles and had a great time. \nThis time I walked out a good bit barefoot since it\'s only 6 inches deep of nice salty warm bath water. The salty mud under the water is really slippery and it was kinda funny to see some people try to follow me out and bite it.\n\nI think we\'re going try to hang here for the evening in hopes to see the Milky Way! \n#fulltimers #fulltimerv #fulltimefamilies #nomads #ditchingsuburbia #utah #water #reflection #bluesky #bonnevillesaltflats'
