          'description': 'BFE Nevada\nWe had a a nice trek across Northern Nevada today. Stopped at every rest area along the way to stretch our legs, hydrate, grab snacks, fly the kite and of course snap a few photos. We ended up in Elko, NV for the evening to make some supply runs since this is the first civilization we\'ve seen in a couple of days. Heck, we\'ve seen more cotton tail rabbits than we have people! \n#fulltimers #fulltimefamilies #nevada #bluesky #clouds #desert #gorving #nomads'
